import {Dropdown as BDropdowm} from 'react-bootstrap/Dropdown';

export default function Dropdown() {
    return <BDropdowm>
        <BDropdowm.Toggle variant="success" id="dropdown-basic">
            Dropdown Button
        </BDropdowm.Toggle>

        <BDropdowm.Menu>
            <BDropdowm.Item href="#/action-1">Action</BDropdowm.Item>
            <BDropdowm.Item href="#/action-2">Another action</BDropdowm.Item>
            <BDropdowm.Item href="#/action-3">Something else</BDropdowm.Item>
        </BDropdowm.Menu>
    </BDropdowm>

}
